author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Transmontaigne Partners L.P. Announces $0.015 Increase In Quarterly Distribution
text:
23 PM / Updated 8 minutes ago BRIEF-Transmontaigne Partners L.P. Announces $0.015 Increase In Quarterly Distribution Reuters Staff 
April 17 (Reuters) - TransMontaigne Partners LP: 
* TRANSMONTAIGNE PARTNERS L.P. ANNOUNCES $0.015 INCREASE IN QUARTERLY DISTRIBUTION 
* TRANSMONTAIGNE PARTNERS LP - DECLARED A DISTRIBUTION OF $0.785 PER UNIT FOR PERIOD FROM JANUARY 1, 2018 THROUGH MARCH 31, 2018 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
